        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JM for trouble taken with French edition [of <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>].</p>  
<p>Is glad 3000 copies of 2d ed. [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>] will be printed.</p> 
